data.description: A must see! With wood flooring throughout the main house, this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath & finished basement is move-in ready. The kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, new dishwasher & new stove top.  Half bath in basement, as well as a washer & dryer hookup. The vacant cottage print shop in back is AS-IS. Full bath & potential 1-2 bedroom. Great opportunity for investors!  Easy access to the GS parkway & I-78. Low taxes. Make this one yours today!
